
Comment:  Which P-flag and Mask-bits to set when a player changes status...
Comment:  The higher levels inherit bits from lower.

PflagApprentice:
  Resurrect Stats WreckDoors Reset SummonObj Weather Lock Trace Peace
  NoHassle TitleEdit Emote Aberchat;

PflagWizard:
  NoTrace NoSnoop NoZap NoSummon NoSteal NoForce NoAlias MflagEdit
  ObjectEdit Heal AliasMob StartInvis RoomEdit Clone Punt Timeout Load/Store 
  Echo NoExorcise NoBurn Burn Sic Goto Zap Exorcise SflagSee;

MaskWizard:
  NoExorcise;

PflagProphet:
  Raw SeeSocket SeeHost PuntAll;

PflagArchWizard:
  UAFInfo PflagEdit AliasPlayers Frob ChMobData Snoop ChScore ChLevel
  NoProbation;

PflagAvatar:
  Reboot SflagEdit Shutdown Ban SeeUser Probation SeeAnon;

PflagGod:
  MaskEdit IgnoreNoAt NoPunt NoForget EflagEdit TextRaw PZap
  NoSic CanLog FList NflagEdit ChatMod Socket NoTimeOut SeeIdle ViewCom
  Syslog;

MaskGod:
  IgnoreNoAt;

PflagMaster:
  Signal;
